**IMPORTANT**
INPUT THIS INTO YOUR TERMINAL TO SETUP THE LIVE ENVIRONMENT 

If you are using VSCODE, input this into the VSCODE terminal to setup your environment 

$ mkdir binance_crypto_trading
$ cd binance_crypto_trading
$ pip install virtualenv

# here crypto is our virtual env, but you can use any name here
$ virtualenv crypto
$ source crypto/bin/activate    # activate the virtual env
